author: Odeinoichus
title: Sporty Shades.
review:
Set #41775 Shades Unikitty: This beach lounging variant of Unikitty can also be found on vacation. She matches her brother in that she's wearing sunglasses on her face. The print on her torso brick however shows an outfit with flower prints and back pockets to store stuff in.

Shades Unikitty is an interesting looking variant with the same parts as most of the other buildable characters in the line. As a fan of the character you can't go wrong with more variants of Unikitty, that being said the lack of unique parts made this series tough to collect. Recommended for Fans.
